room_title: Escape room "DEA" by Suite 201 Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 6819 Sepulveda Blvd, Suite 201 Van Nuys, CA 91405
room_description: Hector and Santiago are two undercover DEA agents who have infiltrated the Colombian cartel and helped capture one of the most powerful and wanted drug lord of all time. As their operation was a success, the cartel lost no time in figuring out who the traitors were and captured Hector and Santiago before they left the country. Do you and your team have what it takes to locate our agents before they get murdered?
